doctype html
html(lang='ru', itemtype='https://schema.org/Person', itemscope)
  head
    title Misha
    meta(name='description', content='Contacts and projects of Mikhael Khrustik')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/hero/hero.scss')
    include ../head.pug
  body
    include ../worker.pug
    .hero
      .hero-header
        h1.hero-heading Let's make<br> cool stuff
        picture.hero-avatar(width='155px', height='155px')
          source(srcset='/photo/avatar@2x.webp 2x, /photo/avatar.webp', type='image/webp')
          img.hero-avatar(src='/photo/avatar.jpg', srcset='/photo/avatar@2x.jpg 2x, /photo/avatar.jpg', alt='Mikhael Khrustik photo', itemprop='image')
      .hero-content
        p
          | Hi, my name is
          | #[span(itemprop='givenName') Mikhael]
          | #[span(itemprop='familyName') Khrustik],
          |  I'm a front lead and developer at
          | #[a(href='https://tektosoft.ru/') Tektosoft].
          | I live in St. Petersburg.
        p
          | Before that, I worked at #[a(href='https://belvg.com') BelVG],
          | #[a(href='https://cmtscience.ru/') CMT],
          | #[a(href='https://cifra.in/') Cifra] and
          | #[a(href='https://efo.ru/') EFO].
          | Was in charge of projects for #[a(href='https://latona.pro/') Latona],
          | #[a(href='https://web.archive.org/web/20180316073843/http://neochemicals.ru/') Neochemicals]
          | and #[a(href='https://chtk.ru/') CHTK].
        p
          | Drawing design, do layout, automating everything.
          | I like to take on difficult tasks that others would prefer to abandon.
        p.hero-footer
          | More information in #[a(href='/en/resume.pug') resume]. <br>
          | Write offers to the email:
          | #[a(href='mailto:misha@myrt.co', itemprop='email') misha@myrt.co], <br>
          | or Telegram: #[a(href='https://t.me/mishamyrt', itemprop='sameAs', rel='me') @mishamyrt]. <br>
          | Ещё я говорю #[a(href='/ru/index.pug') на русском языке].
        .hero-icons
          a.hero-icon(href='https://www.instagram.com/mishamyrt/', itemprop='sameAs', rel='me')
            | Instagram
            include ../hero/icons/instagram.svg
          a.hero-icon(href='https://t.me/mishamyrt', itemprop='sameAs', rel='me')
            | Telegram
            include ../hero/icons/telegram.svg
          a.hero-icon(href='https://gitlab.com/mishamyrt', itemprop='sameAs', rel='me')
            | GitLab
            include ../hero/icons/gitlab.svg
          a.hero-icon(href='https://github.com/mishamyrt', itemprop='sameAs', rel='me')
            | GitHub
            include ../hero/icons/github.svg
          a.hero-icon(href='https://keybase.io/mishamyrt', itemprop='sameAs', rel='me')
            | Keybase
            include ../hero/icons/keybase.svg
